Known Bugs
----------

  OSS sound segfaults with some sound drivers. %-<
  SDL sound code is alpha, and doesn't work for everyone. %-<

  matrox G200 : GL games don't display menus correctly (matrox GL bug ?)

  glh2mp:   The fire weapon for the Demoness in GL mode draws lines across
	    the screen. So does the fire attack of Praevus.

